  <brief_title>Optimal Timing of Dronedarone Initiation After Conversion in Patients With Persistent Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARTEMIS Load</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, International, Multi-center, Open-label Study to Document Optimal Timing of Initiation of Dronedarone Treatment After Conversion With Loading Dose of Amiodarone in Patients With Persistent Atrial Fibrillation Requiring Conversion of AF.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
